INSTALLATION

    To install Perl::Refactor with C<make> give the following
    commands to your favorite shell:

        tar -zxf Perl-Refactor-1.121.tar.gz
        cd Perl-Refactor-1.121
        perl Makefile.PL
        make
        make test
        make install

    Or if you prefer C<Module::Build>, try this:

        tar -zxf Perl-Refactor-1.121.tar.gz
        cd Perl-Refactor-1.121
        perl Build.pl
        ./Build
        ./Build test
        ./Build install


